{"tid":895620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英美關注馬凱被拒入境 英大臣斥破壞言論新聞自由","createTime":"2018-11-09T10:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T01:40:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4acc933e444ccca06ad3cc5b2146c8cfb48b08d7","tid":895620,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"英國外交部亞太事務國務大臣田銘祺（Mark Field）在Twitter表示，非常關注事件，指事件破壞《中英聯合聲明》及《基本法》保障的言論自由及新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港領事館表示，港府至今仍未向馬凱解釋被拒入境原因，田銘祺今早按原定行程來港，已與《金融時報》人員會面，強調會向港府緊急跟進事件。田銘祺下午亦在Twitter上載與《金融時報》亞洲新聞編輯Jamil Anderlini會面的相片。田銘祺去年8月亦曾來港，與本地傳媒見面。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港領事館亦有回應事件，說法大致與上次馬凱被拒續簽證一樣，認為事件嚴重令人不安，批評港府此決定令人感到憂慮，這情況使人聯想到國際新聞從業員在內地面對的問題，有關做法亦不符基本法中相關原則。"},{"pid":"9ac66acd201b7b736ebec3b17a38353ec6b4aac2","tid":895620,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932b4f859361d317db9dcbb4bbf317195f7c68f1","tid":895620,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"一早無咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f0138b00883813fe5f1480f0036ae0c8de96b","tid":895620,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a9ac10ca45f499d13fea4aadde4e16ca3addd6d","tid":895620,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365484fb673ae6b926d9692a84e5c105cfb1446","tid":895620,"uid":11055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"走住黎屌有撚用咩鷹狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母香港冇閪左言論自由好撚多年啦"},{"pid":"a177b397450ad43f2bfb