安局長入唔入到英美境呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9371bc1808e535a96cfff8e5e6dfae7cdeae7e3","tid":895620,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"美靜左一排中期選舉,英就煩緊脫勾<br />\n支那就係咁搞小動作,睇下你仲玩得幾耐<br />\n1月1就25%稅,新年D工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c81025e2758fc027e985a1af2b7a2392c62609","tid":895620,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"係呀，咁點？"},{"pid":"42033f35d378442199d2c995f82e12b093decc87","tid":895620,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭：一國兩制運行良好　英國不會收回香港<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭今午（十八日）一時在「UK in Hong Kong」Facebook專頁進行問答直播，最多港人提出的「英國會否取回香港？」問題被安排在第一條發問，吳若蘭直接了當地回答不會。她補充，英政府在四、五十年前便想過這一點，事實上香港確實屬於中華人民共和國，因此才與其構思了「一國兩制」的框架。她形容自主權移交後的二十年內，「一國兩制」運行得非常良好 （incredibly well），雖然香港與中國面對很多挑戰，但有絕對信心香港能克服它們，繼續繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fuk-will-not-take-back-hk%2F&d=AikRqUF0ABqfijWhCN2gDW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6dc9fa0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/</a>"},{"pid":"c67c491f41849099516d31a27b8eeacd3002ed22","tid":895620,"uid":192068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42033f35d378442199d2c995f82e12b093decc87","tid":895620,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭：一國兩制運行良好　英國不會收回香港<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭今午（十八日）一時在「UK in Hong Kong」Facebook專頁進行問答直播，最多港人提出的「英國會否取回香港？」問題被安排在第一條發問，吳若蘭直接了當地回答不會。她補充，英政府在四、五十年前便想過這一點，事實上香港確實屬於中華人民共和國，因此才與其構思了「一國兩制」的框架。她形容自主權移交後的二十年內，「一國兩制」運行得非常良好 （incredibly well），雖然香港與中國面對很多挑戰，但有絕對信心香港能克服它們，繼續繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fuk-will-not-take-back-hk%2F&d=AikRqUF0ABqfijWhCN2gDW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6dc9fa0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"18/8/2016<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4b9f3df29c89a582d3a3115a625e2a421498f8","tid":895620,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a177b397450ad43f2bfba085629ecea9694232f0","tid":895620,"uid":35930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"Field 居然譯姓田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"springfield 花花幼稚園"},{"pid":"dd36f3ff4b6b9fea213469ea198f848b0efa66d6","tid":895620,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c67c491f41849099516d31a27b8eeacd3002ed22","tid":895620,"uid":192068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42033f35d378442199d2c995f82e12b093decc87","tid":895620,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭：一國兩制運行良好　英國不會收回香港<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港澳總領事吳若蘭今午（十八日）一時在「UK in Hong Kong」Facebook專頁進行問答直播，最多港人提出的「英國會否取回香港？」問題被安排在第一條發問，吳若蘭直接了當地回答不會。她補充，英政府在四、五十年前便想過這一點，事實上香港確實屬於中華人民共和國，因此才與其構思了「一國兩制」的框架。她形容自主權移交後的二十年內，「一國兩制」運行得非常良好 （incredibly well），雖然香港與中國面對很多挑戰，但有絕對信心香港能克服它們，繼續繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fuk-will-not-take-back-hk%2F&d=AikRqUF0ABqfijWhCN2gDW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6dc9fa0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/08/uk-will-not-take-back-hk/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"18/8/2016<img src=\"/assets/face